Interface IStatelessComponentScheduler<L,A,M>

  • Type Parameters:
    L - The listener type.
    A - The action type.
    M - The Message type.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StatelessCallbackScheduler

    public interface IStatelessComponentScheduler<L,A,M>
    Handles instances of a state less component; delegates message to a non blocked component instance or if all components are blocked message is delegated to queue in one of existing instances
